SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AccessFailedCount], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[DOB], [t].[Email], [t].[EmailConfirmed], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HireDate], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastName], [t].[LockoutEnabled], [t].[LockoutEnd], [t].[MiddleName], [t].[NormalizedEmail], [t].[NormalizedUserName], [t].[PasswordHash], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t].[SecurityStamp], [t].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t].[UserName], [t0].[JobUserTaskId], [t0].[JobId], [t0].[UserId], [t0].[TaskId], [t0].[JobId0], [t0].[ActualCost], [t0].[CreatedAt], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[EstimatedCost], [t0].[JobDescription], [t0].[JobStatus], [t0].[JobTitle], [t0].[LastUpdatedDate], [t0].[Priority], [t0].[StartDate], [t0].[TaskId0], [t0].[CompletedDate], [t0].[CreatedAt0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[DueDate], [t0].[Notes], [t0].[Priority0], [t0].[Status], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UpdatedAt], [t2].[JobUserNoteId], [t2].[JobId], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[NoteId], [t2].[JobId0], [t2].[ActualCost], [t2].[CreatedAt], [t2].[EndDate], [t2].[EstimatedCost], [t2].[JobDescription], [t2].[JobStatus], [t2].[JobTitle], [t2].[LastUpdatedDate], [t2].[Priority], [t2].[StartDate], [t2].[NoteId0], [t2].[CreatedAt0], [t2].[Note]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[DOB], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[FirstName], [a].[HireDate], [a].[IsActive], [a].[LastName], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[MiddleName], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [j].[JobUserTaskId], [j].[JobId], [j].[UserId], [j].[TaskId], [j0].[JobId] AS [JobId0], [j0].[ActualCost], [j0].[CreatedAt], [j0].[EndDate], [j0].[EstimatedCost], [j0].[JobDescription], [j0].[JobStatus], [j0].[JobTitle], [j0].[LastUpdatedDate], [j0].[Priority], [j0].[StartDate], [t1].[TaskId] AS [TaskId0], [t1].[CompletedDate], [t1].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[DueDate], [t1].[Notes], [t1].[Priority] AS [Priority0], [t1].[Status], [t1].[Title], [t1].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [JobUserTasks] AS [j]
    INNER JOIN [Jobs] AS [j0] ON [j].[JobId] = [j0].[JobId]
    INNER JOIN [Tasks] AS [t1] ON [j].[TaskId] = [t1].[TaskId]

            FROM

                FROM AspNetUsers AS a
                WHERE a.Id == @__id_0
            ) AS t
            LEFT JOIN 
            (
                SELECT j.JobUserTaskId, j.JobId, j.UserId, j.TaskId, j0.JobId AS JobId0, j0.ActualCost, j0.CreatedAt, j0.EndDate, j0.EstimatedCost, j0.JobDescription, j0.JobStatus, j0.JobTitle, j0.LastUpdatedDate, j0.Priority, j0.StartDate, t1.TaskId AS TaskId0, t1.CompletedDate, t1.CreatedAt AS CreatedAt0, t1.Description, t1.DueDate, t1.Notes, t1.Priority AS Priority0, t1.Status, t1.Title, t1.UpdatedAt
                FROM JobUserTasks AS j
                INNER JOIN Jobs AS j0 ON j.JobId == j0.JobId
                INNER JOIN Tasks AS t1 ON j.TaskId == t1.TaskId
            ) AS t0 ON t.Id == t0.UserId
            LEFT JOIN 
            (

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[UserId]

        SELECT j.JobId, j.ActualCost, j.CreatedAt, j.EndDate, j.EstimatedCost, j.JobDescription, j.JobStatus, j.JobTitle, j.LastUpdatedDate, j.Priority, j.StartDate, t0.JobUserTaskId, t0.JobId, t0.UserId, t0.TaskId, t0.TaskId0, t0.CompletedDate, t0.CreatedAt, t0.Description, t0.DueDate, t0.Notes, t0.Priority, t0.Status, t0.Title, t0.UpdatedAt, t0.Id, t0.AccessFailedCount, t0.ConcurrencyStamp, t0.DOB, t0.Email, t0.EmailConfirmed, t0.FirstName, t0.HireDate, t0.ImageUrl, t0.IsActive, t0.LastName, t0.LockoutEnabled, t0.LockoutEnd, t0.MiddleName, t0.NormalizedEmail, t0.NormalizedUserName, t0.PasswordHash, t0.PhoneNumber, t0.PhoneNumberConfirmed, t0.SecurityStamp, t0.TwoFactorEnabled, t0.UserName, t1.JobUserNoteId, t1.JobId, t1.UserId, t1.NoteId, t1.NoteId0, t1.CreatedAt, t1.Note, t1.Id, t1.AccessFailedCount, t1.ConcurrencyStamp, t1.DOB, t1.Email, t1.EmailConfirmed, t1.FirstName, t1.HireDate, t1.ImageUrl, t1.IsActive, t1.LastName, t1.LockoutEnabled, t1.LockoutEnd, t1.MiddleName, t1.NormalizedEmail, t1.NormalizedUserName, t1.PasswordHash, t1.PhoneNumber, t1.PhoneNumberConfirmed, t1.SecurityStamp, t1.TwoFactorEnabled, t1.UserName, t2.JobId, t2.CustomerId, t2.CustomerJobsId, t2.CustomerId0, t2.Address, t2.City, t2.ContactPerson, t2.CustomerType, t2.Email, t2.Fax, t2.Industry, t2.Name, t2.Notes, t2.Phone, t2.State, t2.Status, t2.Website, t2.ZipCode
        FROM Jobs AS j
        LEFT JOIN 
        (
            SELECT j0.JobUserTaskId, j0.JobId, j0.UserId, j0.TaskId, t.TaskId AS TaskId0, t.CompletedDate, t.CreatedAt, t.Description, t.DueDate, t.Notes, t.Priority, t.Status, t.Title, t.UpdatedAt, a.Id, a.AccessFailedCount, a.ConcurrencyStamp, a.DOB, a.Email, a.EmailConfirmed, a.FirstName, a.HireDate, a.ImageUrl, a.IsActive, a.LastName, a.LockoutEnabled, a.LockoutEnd, a.MiddleName, a.NormalizedEmail, a.NormalizedUserName, a.PasswordHash, a.PhoneNumber, a.PhoneNumberConfirmed, a.SecurityStamp, a.TwoFactorEnabled, a.UserName
            FROM JobUserTasks AS j0
            INNER JOIN Tasks AS t ON j0.TaskId == t.TaskId
            INNER JOIN AspNetUsers AS a ON j0.UserId == a.Id
        ) AS t0 ON j.JobId == t0.JobId
        LEFT JOIN 
        (

        (
            SELECT j0.JobUserTaskId, j0.JobId, j0.UserId, j0.TaskId, t.TaskId AS TaskId0, t.CompletedDate, t.CreatedAt, t.Description, t.DueDate, t.Notes, t.Priority, t.Status, t.Title, t.UpdatedAt, a.Id, a.AccessFailedCount, a.ConcurrencyStamp, a.DOB, a.Email, a.EmailConfirmed, a.FirstName, a.HireDate, a.ImageUrl, a.IsActive, a.LastName, a.LockoutEnabled, a.LockoutEnd, a.MiddleName, a.NormalizedEmail, a.NormalizedUserName, a.PasswordHash, a.PhoneNumber, a.PhoneNumberConfirmed, a.SecurityStamp, a.TwoFactorEnabled, a.UserName

            INNER JOIN AspNetUsers AS a0 ON j1.UserId == a0.Id
        ) AS t1 ON j.JobId == t1.JobId
        LEFT JOIN 
        (
            SELECT c.JobId, c.CustomerId, c.CustomerJobsId, c0.CustomerId AS CustomerId0, c0.Address, c0.City, c0.ContactPerson, c0.CustomerType, c0.Email, c0.Fax, c0.Industry, c0.Name, c0.Notes, c0.Phone, c0.State, c0.Status, c0.Website, c0.ZipCode
            FROM CustomerJobs AS c
            INNER JOIN Customers AS c0 ON c.CustomerId == c0.CustomerId
        ) AS t2 ON j.JobId == t2.JobId

    INNER JOIN [Tasks] AS [t] ON [j0].[TaskId] = [t].[TaskId]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [j0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [j].[JobId] = [t0].[JobId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [j1].[JobUserNoteId], [j1].[JobId], [j1].[UserId], [j1].[NoteId], [n].[NoteId] AS [NoteId0], [n].[CreatedAt], [n].[Note], [a0].[Id], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[DOB], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[HireDate], [a0].[ImageUrl], [a0].[IsActive], [a0].[LastName], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[MiddleName], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName]
    FROM [JobUserNotes] AS [j1]
    INNER JOIN [Notes] AS [n] ON [j1].[NoteId] = [n].[NoteId]
    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [j1].[UserId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [j].[JobId] = [t1].[JobId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[JobId], [c].[CustomerId], [c].[CustomerJobsId], [c0].[CustomerId] AS [CustomerId0], [c0].[Address], [c0].[City], [c0].[ContactPerson], [c0].[CustomerType], [c0].[Email], [c0].[Fax], [c0].[Industry], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Notes], [c0].[Phone], [c0].[State], [c0].[Status], [c0].[Website], [c0].[ZipCode]
    FROM [CustomerJobs] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [c].[CustomerId] = [c0].[CustomerId]
) AS [t2] ON [j].[JobId] = [t2].[JobId]
ORDER BY [j].[JobId], [t0].[JobUserTaskId], [t0].[JobId], [t0].[UserId], [t0].[TaskId], [t0].[TaskId0], [t0].[Id], [t1].[JobUserNoteId], [t1].[JobId], [t1].[UserId], [t1].[NoteId], [t1].[NoteId0], [t1].[Id], [t2].[JobId], [t2].[CustomerId], [t2].[CustomerJobsId]
